  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595971928577-QSY3UUC8TAT885F1E161/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>It was so fun teaching at <a href=\"http://www.scrapbookandcards.com/crop-and-create\">Crop &amp; Create</a> in Markham earlier this month. It was my first time teaching in Canada and I just loved every bit. The event was put on by <a href=\"http://www.scrapbookandcards.com/\">Scrapbook &amp; Cards Today Magazine</a>, which is celebrating 10 years this month! So grateful to Catherine for having me and shuttling me around so I could be on <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2016/3/10/the-marilyn-denis\">the Marilyn Denis Show</a> too. I didn't take nearly enough photos, but I did make <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XirPs_9yJVE\">an entire video</a>, so I hope it feels like you were along for the ride.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972025173-1XXFBWF4TE0DIX1FRMTT/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Had lunch with some of the <a href=\"http://www.kincommunity.com/\">Kin Community</a> Canada team at <a href=\"http://www.tbto.ca/\">Thoroughbred</a>. Then Catherine snapped this behind the scenes look while I was filming just after finishing setting up the gallery wall for the show. Love my Canon G7X for filming, and it's what I use to shoot all my videos.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972044648-ODT1BN9C2815ENIV77TK/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I taught two classes on Saturday, did a make and take Saturday night (then crashed so hard out of creative exhaustion)! I taught my last class on Sunday. It was absolutely wonderful meeting so many creative and uplifting women who share a love for memory keeping. Connecting in person is often hard to describe in words and capture in photos, but trust me, if you have the chance to meet other like-minded amazing people in person, I suggest you do it! Everyone was so nice and full of smiles and I had the best time with them.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"9d-Crop+&amp;+Create+Markham.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972083795-G5HKMQEW51SBQEQ0QH6R/9d-Crop%2B%26%2BCreate%2BMarkham.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"9e-Crop+&amp;+Create+Markham.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972084498-5VODR3UY1LO9ZF3R6FB0/9e-Crop%2B%26%2BCreate%2BMarkham.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"9f-Crop+&amp;+Create+Markham.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972087686-IVKYE76LP7NZKWJFFO73/9f-Crop%2B%26%2BCreate%2BMarkham.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9g-download.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972086219-E8JFR7B88N5T5ZNLSU92/9g-download.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>After I was done teaching on Sunday, I hung out in the crop room and had a 3 week old baby fall asleep in my arms!! It was bliss!</p><p>I even got to see some family for just a minute. Well, technically we aren't related but I did grow up with the lady in the glasses as my aunt basically. My mom and her went to school together in India. Growing up I lived in Chicago and remember more than a few 11+ hour drives to Toronto to visit. She also has twin daughters who happen to be in Cabo or somewhere exotic like that, so unfortunately I didn't get to see them but I did get to see their little sister, Jessica, which was super fun!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972122846-I7262K428JW40ZKUSV2S/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Also so thankful that the weather was not too cold - just about 17 degrees, but not snowing too much and pretty manageable considering I spent most of my time indoors. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"9i-Toronto.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972154451-6BAGU3KJ26YIM159KWZX/9i-Toronto.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9j-Catherine,+Amy+and+Vicki.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595972155360-NAJ3ALGFG41UA0UR6ZJF/9j-Catherine%2C%2BAmy%2Band%2BVicki.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Too much fun!! I'm trying to convince <a href=\"http://vickiboutin.typepad.com/\">Vicky Boutin</a> she needs her own YouTube channel. For those who have met her in person, I know you'd totally agree with me. She's not only hilarious, but just an amazing human being with incredible energy. Loved being around her and all the awesome people at Crop &amp; Create Markham. Already hoping to teach again at a future event!</p><p>There's a giveaway in celebration of 10 years on <a href=\"http://scrapbookandcardstodaymag.typepad.com/scrapbook_cards_today_blo/2016/03/10th-birthday-celebration-day-seven.html\">Scrapbook &amp; Cards Today</a>'s blog, so be sure to check that out!</p><p>This blog post was fun to put together, and I am really going to try and be better about recaps and keeping you all updated on stuff that's going on. The videos on <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AmyTangerineSub\">YouTube</a> have just taken up a lot of time and then I feel like I am being repetitive when I type stuff out. Perhaps I will share the photos of the traveler's notebook once I print my pictures and finish it up. Let me know what you think in the comments below! Enjoy <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XirPs_9yJVE\">the video</a>!</p>"
}